: Attack, Defense, and Health Points. Over the course of battles, these attributes can be enhanced with different types of boosters, adding a strategic layer to each encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/bf8fcec550e73a1fe4f19a3359eeb07c.poster.avif?t=1735663811\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/bf8fcec550e73a1fe4f19a3359eeb07c.webm?t=1735663811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/bf8fcec550e73a1fe4f19a3359eeb07c.mp4?t=1735663811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully build your deck from the 720 unlockable cards to chain together as many battles as possible. The more opponents you face during an adventure, the more valuable the final reward will be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/d653faa8510b8b71e6dccd896ddc16bb.poster.avif?t=1735663811\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/d653faa8510b8b71e6dccd896ddc16bb.webm?t=1735663811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/d653faa8510b8b71e6dccd896ddc16bb.mp4?t=1735663811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use these rewards to strengthen your deck and attempt to face the elites of the southern district.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/d686a0899591017d2b337177b30f318a.poster.avif?t=1735663811\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/d686a0899591017d2b337177b30f318a.webm?t=1735663811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350480/extras/d686a0899591017d2b337177b30f318a.mp4?t=1735663811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
